article.description: — Josh Oduro had 22 points as George Mason routed Morgan State 90-53 on Sunday night.
article.headline: Oduro scores 22 to carry George Mason past Morgan St. 90-53
article.linkText: Oduro scores 22 to carry George Mason past Morgan St. 90-53
article.story: FAIRFAX, Va. -- — Josh Oduro had 22 points as George Mason routed Morgan State 90-53 on Sunday night. D'Shawn Schwartz had 17 points and seven rebounds for George Mason (3-0). Davonte Gaines added 15 points and eight rebounds. Devon Cooper had 14 points. De'Torrion Ware had 15 points for the Bears (2-1). Keith McGee added 14 points.
